flowchart TD
    Start([Webhook Diterima POST /api/webhook/midtrans])
    Start --> IpCheck{IP Whitelist?}
    IpCheck -->|Not Whitelisted| Reject403([HTTP 403 Forbidden])
    IpCheck -->|Whitelisted| Verify{Verifikasi Signature Key?}
    Verify -->|Invalid| Reject403
    Verify -->|Valid| Return200([HTTP 200 OK - Segera])
    Return200 --> Dispatch[Dispatch Job ke Queue]

    Dispatch --> Job[Job: ProcessMidtransWebhook]
    Job --> Idempotent{Cek order_id<br>status bukan Pending?}
    Idempotent -->|Sudah diproses| Skip([Skip - Idempotent])
    Idempotent -->|Belum| GetStatus[GET /v2/order_id/status\Verifikasi Sekunder ke Midtrans API]

    GetStatus --> FraudCheck{Fraud Status?}
    FraudCheck -->|challenge| TreatFail[Perlakukan sebagai Failed]
    FraudCheck -->|accept| Map[Map transaction_status]

    Map -->|settlement/capture| Settle[TransitionOrderStatus → Settlement]
    Map -->|expire| Expired[TransitionOrderStatus → Expire]
    Map -->|cancel| Canceled[TransitionOrderStatus → Cancel]
    Map -->|deny/failure| Failed[TransitionOrderStatus → Failed]
    Map -->|refund/partial_refund| Refund[TransitionOrderStatus → RefundPending]
    Map -->|pending| Pending[Skip - tetap Pending]

    Settle --> Audit[Insert order_status_logs]
    Expired --> Audit
    Canceled --> Audit
    Failed --> Audit
    Refund --> Audit
    TreatFail --> Failed

    Audit --> StockEffect{Stock Effect?}
    StockEffect -->|settlement| DeductReserved[deduct_reserved:<br>Kurangi stock & stock_reserved<br>Increment total_sold]
    StockEffect -->|expire/cancel/failed| ReleaseReserved[release_reserved / restore_stock:<br>Kembalikan stok]
    StockEffect -->|refund| Done

    DeductReserved --> Done([Selesai])
    ReleaseReserved --> Done
    Pending --> Done


